Text: RICETMSKean I assume that you have received my letter and enclosed information of November If that material prompted any questions I will answer them promptly I hope that with your continuing involvement that we can fund some of these scholarships through the generosity of Enron executives such as yourself Thanks for your continuing interest CMacDowell
